The main brush makes abnormal noise:
1.Check whether there is any foreign object entangled in the main brush and clean it up ;
2.If there is a spare main brush, you can cross-test
3.If the above cannot solve the problem, manually rotate the main brush to determine if it is an abnormal sound from the main brush gearbox, and send it for repair to replace the main brush assembly;

The main brush does not rotate/the voice:
1.Check whether there is any foreign object entangled in the main brush and remove it ;
2.If the error message persists, replace the main brush with a new one for cross-testing;
3.If the error persists, reset the machine
4.If replacing the main brush assembly still does not solve the problem, send it back to the repair center to replace the main board.
Spare parts involved: main brush, main brush assembly, main board
